<h1>Lists</h1>

<p>Lists are used to display collections of records.</p>

<h2>Simple Usage</h2>

<p>This is a simple list containing just a title for each item.</p>

{{#docs-demo as |demo|}}

  {{#demo.example name="lists"}}

    {{#uxs-list as |list|}}
      {{#each items as |thing|}}
        {{#list.item as |item|}}
          {{item.title thing.title}}
        {{/list.item}}
      {{/each}}
    {{/uxs-list}}

  {{/demo.example}}

  {{demo.snippet "lists.hbs"}}

{{/docs-demo}}

<h2>Adding more content</h2>

<p>This is a list contains some meta data and includes a bottom border. By defining the lines & border property on the list component, these properties are passed to each item and will set the height and bottom-border.</p>

{{#docs-demo as |demo|}}

  {{#demo.example name="bordered-list"}}

    {{#uxs-list lines=2 bordered=true as |list|}}
      {{#each items as |thing|}}
        {{#list.item as |item|}}
          {{#item.content}}
            {{item.title thing.title}}
            {{item.content thing.location}}
          {{/item.content}}
        {{/list.item}}
      {{/each}}
    {{/uxs-list}}

  {{/demo.example}}

  {{demo.snippet "bordered-list.hbs"}}

{{/docs-demo}}

<h2>Avatars and Actions</h2>

<p>This is a list that includes some horizontal layout for the avatar and item. We use the aside and body contextual components to split up each items layout.</p>

{{#docs-demo as |demo|}}

  {{#demo.example name="action-list"}}

    {{#uxs-list lines=3 bordered=true as |list|}}
      {{#each items as |thing|}}
        {{#list.item as |item|}}
          {{#item.aside}}
            {{item.avatar "https://placeimg.com/100/100/any" round=true}}
          {{/item.aside}}
          {{#item.body}}
            {{item.title thing.title}}
            {{item.detail thing.location}}
            {{item.detail thing.email}}
          {{/item.body}}
          {{#item.aside}}
            {{item.action "keyboard_arrow_right"}}
          {{/item.aside}}
        {{/list.item}}
      {{/each}}
    {{/uxs-list}}

  {{/demo.example}}

  {{demo.snippet "action-list.hbs"}}

{{/docs-demo}}

